  "description": "A deck is the bounded set of cards used as the core material of play in a [card game](../_index.md). A deck can be standardized — the 52-card French-suited deck (four [suits](./suit.md), thirteen [ranks](./rank.md) each) is the most widely used — or custom to a specific game, as in trading card games and many modern board-adjacent card games.",
